<h1>Appointment Rescheduled</h1>

<p>
Dear <%= @stylist.name %>,
</p>
<p>
The appointment requested by <%= @client.name %> at <%= @salon.name %> has been rescheduled.
The new requested date and time are below.
</p>
<p>
<em>Appointment Details</em><br/>
<%= @salon.name %><br/>
<%= @salon.address %><br/>
<%= @salon.phone %><br/><br/>
Stylist: <%= @stylist.name %><br/>
Date: <%= @appointment.appointment_time.strftime('%m/%d/%Y %l:%M %p') %>
</p>
<p>
	Please click the link below to go to this appointment to review the time
	and confirm, change, or cancel this request.
</p>

<p>
	<%= link_to 'Appointment Details', appointment_url(@appointment) %>
</p>
<p>
	<em>Contact information for <%= @client.name %>:</em><br/>
	<%= @client.email %><br/>
</p>

<hr/>
<p>
	Thank you for using <%= link_to "Madrilla", root_url %> for your appointment booking needs.
</p>


